  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\ntruffle 3.4.6 and 3.4.7 install solc 0.4.13 that introduces bug\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/2621\r\nsolved in \r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/solidity/pull/2652\r\n\r\nCurrent workaround is to install truffle@3.4.5 with solc 0.4.11.\r\nUpstream fixed bug and could be included in solc 0.4.15.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nnpm install truffle@3.4.7\r\n\r\nwrite a contract with a modifier.\r\nDefine a function with two parameters and applies the modifier to both parameters.\r\n\r\nmodifier nonZeroAddress(address x) {\r\n    require(x != 0);\r\n    _;\r\n  }\r\n\r\nfunction X(address a, address b) \r\nnonZeroAddress(a)\r\nnonZeroAddress(b)\r\n{ ... }\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nThe contract should compile.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nThe function will not compile.\r\n\r\n DeclarationError: Modifier already used for this function.\r\n    updateAccount(_to) //update receivers rake before transfer as well, to avoid over-attributing rake\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: \r\n* Truffle version: 3.4.7 and 3.4.6\r\n* Ethereum client:\r\n* node version: 8.2.1\r\n* npm version: 5.3.0\r\n",
